Summary: shooting star falling towards the earth that suddenly ascends w/o decelerating into the sky
divs: Sighting DetailsI was standing outside in my front yard watching the sky because there was an impressive full moon that night when I saw a shooting star,I watched as the shooting star was descending towards the earth when it suddenly did a 180 and ascended into the sky and disappeared. The "shooting star" or whatever it was it didnt decelerate, or turn it just descended, then ascended! What was it??!!!
